  Setup 2/2                                                                     
  Select a verbosity mode for interim transcript items:

  You can change this later via /verbosity.                                     
  Minimal is the default and keeps output compact.                              

  › 1. Minimal (default) — Dim commentary and hide tool chatter
    2. Simple — Show interim items normally

  Press enter to continue
